drop table if exists studentinfo;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: studentinfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table studentinfo
(
id varchar(20) not null,
real_name varchar(10),
scores varchar(10),
university varchar(10),
studentNumber varchar(20),
primary key (id)
);

alter table studentinfo comment '这是用来存储身份为学生的用户的个人身份信息';

alter table studentinfo add constraint FK_Reference_3 foreign key (id)
references account (id) on delete restrict on update restrict;
